\pard\tx566\tx1133\tx1700\tx2267\tx2834\tx3401\tx3968\tx4535\tx5102\tx5669\tx6236\tx6803\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
The sliders numbered 1 through 4 set the range of the (sinc) function shrinking each wavelet independently, with this it is possible to achieve a lot of textures by sweeping your way through the frequency spectrum with each of the pulsars.\
\
PW - This slider affects all wavelets equally, it behaves like the previous sliders but also moves the wavelets out of place in the sequence.\
\
You also have individual CV controls for each of these.\
\
